<br>
She was about to go up and speak to the young man, but then was stopped when she saw the Scynthian warrior walking by with a crate of weapons.  Barely hiding herself behind a building, Alexiares watched for a moment. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=theseusofthemiscrya>Theseus of Themiscrya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#993300>(4/29/03 7:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm65.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Under Watchful Eye</span><hr size=1> Theseus sat under the tree, his eyes watching the activity of the street.  Apollo was starting to set in the West as he noticed a man about his age carrying a large amount of weaponry through the streets.  He would have gotten up to help but the man seemed to have everything under control and there was a certain manner about him that seemed to give off the illusion that he needed no help from anyone.  <br>
<br>
As Theseus began to drink his mead, his eyes drifted off to the left and rested on a young girl hugged up close to a tree.  He smiled watching her as she watched the weapons dealer make his way through the city streets.  He spoke to her, &quot;Would you like some bread and meat?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=alexiares>Alexiares</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#993300>(4/29/03 7:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm65.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/queenhippolyte/images/alexiares.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Under Watchful Eye</span><hr size=1> When the young warrior spoke to her, Alexiares was startled.  She looked to him and then smiled.  Slowely, she slinked her body around the corner of the building and walked up to him.  She was dressed in a sheer blue fabric that flowed around her tanned form like a soft breeze.  Her feet were bare, as Alexiares perferred.  She liked how the dirt and grass felt on her skin.  <br>
<br>
Then stopped a little bit before him and gazed down.  &quot;I hadn't actually been watching you for your lunch.  But, if you don't mind sharing, I could eat a bit.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=theseusofthemiscrya>Theseus of Themiscrya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#993300>(5/1/03 5:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm65.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Sharing Lunch</span><hr size=1> Theseus smiled up at the girl, shrugging lightly, &quot;It's okay, I don't like eating alone anyway.  Please will you join me?&quot;  He scooted slightly to ensure she had plenty of room on the blanket.  His eyes rarely leaving hers, as he extended his hand to her in greeting, &quot;I'm Theseus of Themiscrya.&quot;   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=daughterofshylock>Daughter of Shylock</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.picturesof.net/_wallpaper/rose_Dsc08151_WP.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 328<br> <font color=#993300>(5/1/03 11:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm65.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.picturesof.net/_wallpaper/rose_Dsc08151_WP.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sharing Lunch</span><hr size=1> Wulf overheard the word &quot;Themiscrya&quot; and his eyes looked up at the two.<br>
He gently set the crate down and walked over to where the two people sat.<br>
<br>
&quot;I don't mean to intrude on either of you. But are you Themiscryans?&quot;<br>
<br>
He paused and ran a hand through his shaggy blonde hair.<br>
<br>
&quot;I know it must seem humorous for a man to ask about an amazon village, but I was born and raised there by my Mother, Queen Alysia Loire.&quot; <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">~*~ Jessica ~*~<br>
